  "subject": "Test with 4c-4g build server",
  "commit_message": "Test with 4c-4g build server\n\nAll jjb jobs defined by Jeremy for subprojects in this repo (python)\nfailed.  We suspect this was due to the particular build server \n(8c-8g) being used because these failures occured during pytest\nphase and these tests pass when run by sonar job on 4c-4g server.\nHence making this change to test.\n\nChange-Id: Idf0fa573cf2e6777c40a99523e9df209b818e8b3\nSigned-off-by: Lusheng Ji <lji@research.att.com>\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-206\n",
